com.xively.client.model

Interface DomainObject

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApiKey, Datapoint, Datastream, Feed, Trigger

    public interface DomainObject
    Interface for all resources that can be requested from the API directly. This is super class of all resource objects (in restful API terms) or model object (in MVC terms).
